<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/464510-what-s-with-the-mockingbirds-and-dystopian">what&#39;s with the mockingbirds and dystopian novels?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_464510'><a id="like_count_community_question_464510" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/464510?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">3 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F826824.Mockingbird">like</a></span>

</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionTimestamp'>
<a href="/questions/464510-what-s-with-the-mockingbirds-and-dystopian">6 years ago</a>
</li>
<li class='footerItem communityQuestionPermalink'>
<a href="/questions/464510-what-s-with-the-mockingbirds-and-dystopian">Add your answer</a>
</li>
</ul>
</div>

</div>
<div class='allCommunityAnswers'>
<div class='communityAnswer'>
<div class='communityAnswerBody'>
<div class='answererUserIcon'>
<a class="leftAlignedImage userPhoto" href="/user/show/44471912-gg"><img alt="" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1435901965i/44471912.jpg" /></a>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerTextContainer'>
<span class='communityAnswererName'>
<a href="/user/show/44471912-gg">GG</a>
</span>
<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">Mockingbirds are best known for the habit of some species mimicking the sounds of other birds and animals. In dystopian novels the allegory is that ra<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">Mockingbirds are best known for the habit of some species mimicking the sounds of other birds and animals. In dystopian novels the allegory is that rather than a life richly lived life, the life being lived is but an echo of what life could be, should be, or was. A mockery.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
</div>
</div>
<div class='communityAnswerFooter'>

