        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer99145364" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer17407687962209555">I started Mockingbird because it was on my TBR from 2010, and somehow thought it was a detective novel of sorts. Wrong! It starts with a robot in a robot-dominant landscape who is unable to end his life, and brings in a human who has taught himself to read, something humans no longer do. Then he meets a woman who isn&apos;t on the mind-altering drugs.... Very readable and engaging!</span>
  <span id="freeText17407687962209555" style="display:none">I started Mockingbird because it was on my TBR from 2010, and somehow thought it was a detective novel of sorts. Wrong! It starts with a robot in a robot-dominant landscape who is unable to end his life, and brings in a human who has taught himself to read, something humans no longer do. Then he meets a woman who isn't on the mind-altering drugs.... Very readable and engaging!</span>
  <a data-text-id="17407687962209555" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
