<div class='bookAuthorProfile__about'>

<span id="freeTextContainer6826350890012512591">Walter Stone Tevis was an American novelist and short story writer. Three of his six novels were adapted into major films: The Hustler, The Color of Money and The Man Who Fell to Earth. The Queen&apos;s Gambit has also been adapted in 2020 into a 7-episode mini-series. His books have been translated into at least 18 languages.</span>
  <span id="freeText6826350890012512591" style="display:none">Walter Stone Tevis was an American novelist and short story writer. Three of his six novels were adapted into major films: The Hustler, The Color of Money and The Man Who Fell to Earth. The Queen's Gambit has also been adapted in 2020 into a 7-episode mini-series. His books have been translated into at least 18 languages.</span>
